centralauth-mergeaccount-desc: [[Special:MergeAccount|Merges monie accoonts]] fer Single Uiser Login
centralauth-merge-denied: Sairrie, ye dinna hae permeession tae access this page.
centralauth-merge-notlogged: Please [$1 log in] tae check gif yer accoonts hae been fulie merged.
centralauth-merge-welcome:
'''Yer uiser accoont haesna yet been migrated til the uneefied login system o {{int:Centralauth-groupname}}.'''

Gif ye chuise tae migrate yer accoonts, ye'll be able tae uise the same uisername n passwaird tae log in til aw wikis o {{int:Centralauth-groupname}} in aw available lieds.

Gif some ither bodie haes awreadie taen yer uisername oan anither steid this will na disturb thaim, but it will gie ye ae chance tae wairk it oot wi thaim or wi aen admeenistrater later.
centralauth-merge-step1-detail:
Please enter yer accoont passwaird.
Yer passwaird n registered email address will be checked again the accoonts oan ither wikis tae confirm that thay match.
Nae chynges will be makit ontil ye'v confirmed that things ar in order.
centralauth-merge-step2-detail:
Some o the accoonts coudna be autæmateeclie matched til the designated hame wiki.
Gif thir accoonts belang til ye, ye can confirm that thay ar yers bi providin the passwaird fer thaim.
centralauth-merge-dryrun-complete:
Aw exeestin accoonts can be autæmateeclie uneefied!

Nae chynges hae been makit til yer accoonts yet.
centralauth-merge-dryrun-incomplete:
Ye'r set tae continue, bit some accoonts coudna be autæmateeclie vereefied n willna be migrated immeedeeatelie.
Ye'll be able tae merge thir later.

Nae chynges hae been makit til yer accoonts yet.
centralauth-merge-dryrun-home:
The migration system coudna confirm that ye'r the ainer o the hame wiki accoont fer yer uisername.

Anither wiki wis determined aes the hame accoont fer yer uisername; follae the airtin ablo n log in thaur tae finish yer accoont migration.
centralauth-merge-step3-detail: Ye'r readie tae craft yer uneefied accoont, wi the follaein wikis attached:
centralauth-merge-no-accounts:
Nae accoonts matchin yer name were foond in the central accoont trackin buird!
The database maun be rotten.
centralauth-merge-home-password:
The home wiki fer this accoont (leetit ablo) haes ae differant passwaird til the yin that ye entered.
Please enter the passwaird fer the hame wiki.
centralauth-complete-text: Ye can nou log in til onie wiki steid o {{int:Centralauth-groupname}} wioot cræftin ae new accoont.
centralauth-incomplete-text: Yince yer login is uneefied, ye'll be able tae log in til onie wiki steid o {{int:Centralauth-groupname}} wioot cræftin ae new accoont
centralauth-not-owner-text:
The uisername "$1" wis autæmateeclie assigned til the ainer o the accoont oan $2.

Gif this is ye, that ye can finish the login uneefeecation process bi simplie typin the maister passwaird fer that accoont here:
centralauth-disabled-dryrun:
Accoont uneefeecation is nou in ae demo / debuggin mode, sae actual mergin operations ar disabled.
Sairrie!
centralauth-error-locked: Ye canna eedit cause yer accoont is lockt.
centralauth-error-unmerged: You canna eedit cause yer accoont isna uneefied.
centralauth-list-home-dryrun: The passwaird n email address set at this wiki will be uised fer yer uneefied accoont.
centralauth-list-attached: The accoonts named "$1" oan ilka o the follaein steids hae autæmateeclie been attached til the uneefied accoont:
centralauth-list-attached-dryrun: The accoonts named "$1" oan ilka o the follaein steids will be autæmateeclie attached til the uneefied accoont:

The {{PLURAL:$2|accoont|accoonts}} named "$1" coudna be autæmateeclie confirmed aes belangin til ye oan the follaein {{PLURAL:$2|steid|steids}};
maist likelie {{PLURAL:$2|it haes|thay hae}} ae differant passwaird fae yer primarie accoont:
centralauth-merge-method-primary-desc:
This is the wiki whaur the accoont wis ineetiallie merged.
Mynd that it micht differ fae the real hame wiki o that uiser.
centralauth-merge-method-empty-desc: Indeecates that the local accoont wis merged cause it had nae eedits.
centralauth-merge-method-mail-desc: Indeecates that the local accoont wis merged cause its email address matched the email address o the main accoont.
centralauth-merge-method-password-desc: Indeecates that the local accoont wis merged cause the uiser speceefied ae valid passwaird fer it.
centralauth-merge-method-admin-desc:
Indeecates that the local accoont wis merged manuallie bi stewards.
That feature is disabled nou fer securitie raisons.
centralauth-merge-method-new-desc: Indeecates that the global accoont wis cræftit autæmateeclie whan that local accoont wis cræftit.
centralauth-merge-method-login-desc: Indeecates that the local accoont wis cræftit autæmateeclie whan the uiser logged in.
centralauth-finish-text: Gif thir accoonts dae belang til ye, than ye can finish the login uneefeecation process simplie bi typin the passwairds fer the ither accoonts here:
centralauth-finish-problems:
Ar ye haein troable, or ar ye na the ainer o thir ither accoonts?
[[meta:Special:MyLanguage/Help:Unified login|Hou tae fynd heelp]]…
centralauth-finish-noconfirms: Nae accoonts coud be confirmed uisin this passwaird.
centralauth-finish-incomplete:

Ither accoonts ar na yet confirmed.

centralauth-admin-delete-description:
Delytin the global accoont will delyte onie global preeferances, onattach aw local accoonts, n lea the global name free fer anither uiser tae tak.
Aw local accoonts will continue tae exeest.
The passwairds fer local accoonts cræftit afore the merge will revert til thair pre-merge values.

centralauth-centralautologin-desc:
This byordinair page is uised internallie bi MediaWiki.
Whan ye veesit ae linkt domain while na loggit in, the central login system uises this page tae determine whather ye'r loggit in til the central domain.
Ye'v speired fer this page wioot providin onie authentication data, sae it dis nawthing.
centralauth-centralautologin-notposted: Central login form maun be posted
centralauth-centralautologin-badstate-ce: State "$1" is na valid oan the central wiki
centralauth-centralautologin-badstate-lo: State "$1" is na valid oan the local wiki
centralauth-centralautologin-badwiki: The wiki "$1" is na valid fer central login
centralauth-centralautologin-p3p-explana:
Certain brousers need ae P3P compact policie fer cookies tae be sent or receeved in some cases, incluidin the situation involved in the SUL login check. This is ae needless huip tae jump throoch in this situation, conseederin that aw pages involved ar in the same wiki groop n P3P itsel is maistlie obsileate n abandoned; fortunatelie, the onvalid policie linkin til this page is nou conseedered "guid enooch" bi thir brousers' defaut confeegurations.

Please luikower this steid's person-readable preevacie policie tae determine hou onie information collectit micht be uised.
centralauth-centralautologin-logged-in: Ye'r nou loggit in aes $1. Relaid the page tae applie yer uiser settins.
centralauth-centralautologin-logged-in-n: Ye'r centrallie loggit in. Relaid the page tae applie yer uiser settins.

The follaein global groops hae been confeegured.
Ye can see or eedit the permeessions assigned til ae groop, gif ye'v permeession tae.
Ae groop can be delytit bi remuivin aw richts fae it.

centralauth-finishglobaliseemail_body:
Yer email address haes been set aes assoceeatit wi the accoont "$2" oan aw Wikimedia waurks, wi yer main accoont being oan {{SITENAME}}.

Tae confirm that this accoont reallie dis belang til ye, merge in onie o yer accoonts that we coudna dae autæmateeclie, n permit ye tae recover yer accoont gif ye luise yer passwaird, please apen this link in yer brouser:

$3

Gif the accoont dis *na* belang til ye, follae this link tae cancel the email address confirmation:

$5

This confirmation code will expire oan $6 at $7.

globalrenamerequest-desc: Speir fer ae global accoont rename
globalrenamerequest-forced: The Wikimedia Foundation is [[:mw:SUL_finalisation|uneefyin uisernames across aw Wikimedia waurks]]. This uisername wis identified aes bein in uised oan ither Wikimedia wikis n maun be chynged sae aes tae finalise this uneefication. Cause o this, ye maun pick ae new uisername.
globalrenamerequest-pretext:
Speir fer ae new uisername tae be knawn bi across aw waurks.

Aw o yer aforegaun contreebutions will be connectit wi this new uisername.

Yince ye'v speired fer ae new uisername, ae message will be sent tae Wikimedia stewards tae perform the rename. Ye'l be taud bi email whan this is duin.
globalrenamerequest-newname-help: Enter the new uisername that ye wish tae uise, e.g., "$1".
globalrenamerequest-newname-err-invalid: Ye'v no speceefie'd ae valid uisername.
globalrenamerequest-newname-err-taken: This uisername is awreidie in uiss. Please chuise ae different name.
globalrenamerequest-email-why-explain:
We need aen email address durin this process tae be sair that ye dinna lose access tae this accoont.

Ye can remuiv the email address efter the rename process is duin.
globalrenamerequest-email2-help: Enter the same email address that ye entered abuin fer tae confirm.
globalrenamerequest-email-mismatch:

Please check baith n gie it anither shot.
globalrenamerequest-email-invalid: An onvalid email address wis gien.
globalrenamerequest-save-error: Failed tae hain the speirin. Please gie it anither shot.
globalrenamerequest-status-text:
Yer uisername chynge speirin is nou in progress n is awaitin the approval o a steward. Ye'll be taud bi wa o email whan the speirin haes been processed.

;Uisername the nou:
:$1
;Speired fer uisername:
:$2
